item.title: Contributing
item.description: Contributing to Code Your Future Immersive Go Course This repository is a permissively licensed, open source work. We welcome contributions, both as corrections/improvements and additions, and recommend filing an issue for discussion before investing too much work. Goals This repository primarily exists to help junior software engineers get experience with the Go programming language, and learn about topics that would be useful as a software engineer working in production.
